text: Marc Boudoux (born 3 July 1959) is a French rower. He competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
